# =============================================================================
# GT-KB session overlay runtime (non-authoritative, per-harness)
# =============================================================================
# Overlays are copy-only, non-authoritative context built per session/harness.
# They must never enter version control: canonical state lives in the KB, the
# bridge, MemBase, and the deliberation archive — overlays only surface a
# stale-aware view of already-generated dashboard artifacts. Keeping the root
# ignored also prevents accidental promotion of overlay contents to truth.
.groundtruth/session/overlays/
.groundtruth/session/snapshots/

# Ephemeral session/evaluation artifacts
# (PRODUCTION-READINESS-* files migrated to applications/Agent_Red/pdf-tooling/ in S331 sub-slice 18.B; patterns relocated to PDF Generation section above.)
